criteria.textblock:
        Interventional hospital will be selected based on following criteria:

          1. having complete outpatients and inpatients electronic records;

          2. more than 50% of registrars and/or consultants in the department participated the
             professional education event;

          3. the department head is willing to participate the clinical audit and provide the
             information from outpatients and inpatients records for data collection;

          4. except for rheumatic diseases have been clearly diagnosed.

        Non-interventional hospital will be selected based on following criteria:

          1. having complete outpatients and inpatients electronic records;

          2. no professional education event covered;

          3. the department head is willing to participate the clinical audit and provide the
             information from outpatients and inpatients records for data collection;

          4. except for rheumatic diseases have been clearly diagnosed.
